<paragraph id="C9133691FFE1FFE74DD1FF71FE6493B5" blockId="6.[151,439,151,211]" box="[151,439,186,211]" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">
(
<figureCitation id="51972A14FFE1FFE74DD9FF71FEC893B5" box="[159,283,186,211]" captionStart="FIGURE4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[175,1419,1004,1816]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,988,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE4. Hecalus snipussp. nov. A.PygoPhore, lateral view; B. style, dorsal view; C.connective, dorsal view; D.valve and subgenital Plate, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, dorsal view; F. aedeagus lateral view; G. female seventh sternite, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242046/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Fig. 4A–G</figureCitation>
; Plate IIA–C)
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="81B6651AFFE1FFE74DD1FEC9FAD49139" pageId="6" pageNumber="586" type="description">
<paragraph id="C9133691FFE1FFE74DD1FEC9FDB4927D" blockId="6.[151,1437,258,859]" box="[151,615,258,283]" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">
Length. Male: 
<quantity id="0E549B74FFE1FFE74C7BFEC9FE6C927C" box="[317,447,258,283]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.1" metricValueMax="6.3" metricValueMin="5.9" pageId="6" pageNumber="586" unit="mm" value="6.1" valueMax="6.3" valueMin="5.9">5.9–6.3mm</quantity>
; female: 
<quantity id="0E549B74FFE1FFE74F60FEC8FDB0927D" box="[550,611,259,283]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" pageId="6" pageNumber="586" unit="mm" value="8.0">8mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C9133691FFE1FFE74D81FEEDFBB792E1" blockId="6.[151,1437,258,859]" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">
<emphasis id="FBD8EA83FFE1FFE74D81FEEDFDE19259" bold="true" box="[199,562,294,319]" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Colouration and Morphology:</emphasis>
Stramineous. Crown and face without submarginal fuscous lines (Plate IIA). Crown subangularly produced; broadly triangular with dorsal marginal ridge. Genae strongly sinuate below eyes. Ocelli on margin next to eyes. Pronotum as wide as head, laterally carinate (Plate IIA).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C9133691FFE1FFE74D81FE59FAD49139" blockId="6.[151,1437,258,859]" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">
<emphasis id="FBD8EA83FFE1FFE74D81FE59FEE692CD" bold="true" box="[199,309,402,427]" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Genitalia</emphasis>
: Pygofer lobe subacute apically, heavily setose in posterior half; much straighter at dorsal margin (
<figureCitation id="51972A14FFE1FFE74DD9FE7DFF2992A9" box="[159,250,438,463]" captionStart="FIGURE4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[175,1419,1004,1816]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,988,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE4. Hecalus snipussp. nov. A.PygoPhore, lateral view; B. style, dorsal view; C.connective, dorsal view; D.valve and subgenital Plate, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, dorsal view; F. aedeagus lateral view; G. female seventh sternite, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242046/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Fig. 4A</figureCitation>
). Valve broadly triangular (
<figureCitation id="51972A14FFE1FFE74F69FE7DFD5992A9" box="[559,650,438,463]" captionStart="FIGURE4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[175,1419,1004,1816]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,988,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE4. Hecalus snipussp. nov. A.PygoPhore, lateral view; B. style, dorsal view; C.connective, dorsal view; D.valve and subgenital Plate, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, dorsal view; F. aedeagus lateral view; G. female seventh sternite, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242046/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Fig. 4D</figureCitation>
). Connective “Y”-shaped with short stem (
<figureCitation id="51972A14FFE1FFE74928FE7DFB1B92A9" box="[1134,1224,438,463]" captionStart="FIGURE4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[175,1419,1004,1816]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,988,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE4. Hecalus snipussp. nov. A.PygoPhore, lateral view; B. style, dorsal view; C.connective, dorsal view; D.valve and subgenital Plate, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, dorsal view; F. aedeagus lateral view; G. female seventh sternite, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242046/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Fig. 4C</figureCitation>
). Subgenital plates elongate, broader at base, tapering apically with 8–9 submarginal setae (
<figureCitation id="51972A14FFE1FFE74E91FE11FBE79295" box="[983,1076,474,499]" captionStart="FIGURE4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[175,1419,1004,1816]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,988,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE4. Hecalus snipussp. nov. A.PygoPhore, lateral view; B. style, dorsal view; C.connective, dorsal view; D.valve and subgenital Plate, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, dorsal view; F. aedeagus lateral view; G. female seventh sternite, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242046/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Fig. 4D</figureCitation>
). Style with pointed apophysis; preapical lobe moderately developed (
<figureCitation id="51972A14FFE1FFE74F17FE35FD7E9171" box="[593,685,510,535]" captionStart="FIGURE4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[175,1419,1004,1816]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,988,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE4. Hecalus snipussp. nov. A.PygoPhore, lateral view; B. style, dorsal view; C.connective, dorsal view; D.valve and subgenital Plate, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, dorsal view; F. aedeagus lateral view; G. female seventh sternite, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242046/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Fig. 4B</figureCitation>
). Aedeagus with finger-like dorsal apodeme (
<figureCitation id="51972A14FFE1FFE74984FE35FAC89171" box="[1218,1307,510,535]" captionStart="FIGURE4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[175,1419,1004,1816]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,988,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE4. Hecalus snipussp. nov. A.PygoPhore, lateral view; B. style, dorsal view; C.connective, dorsal view; D.valve and subgenital Plate, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, dorsal view; F. aedeagus lateral view; G. female seventh sternite, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242046/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Fig. 4F</figureCitation>
). Aedeagal shaft nearly straight; with serrations above median length and before apex, with pair of lacerated, subequal apical processes (
<figureCitation id="51972A14FFE1FFE74C57FD8DFEBA9139" box="[273,361,582,607]" captionStart="FIGURE4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[175,1419,1004,1816]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,988,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE4. Hecalus snipussp. nov. A.PygoPhore, lateral view; B. style, dorsal view; C.connective, dorsal view; D.valve and subgenital Plate, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, dorsal view; F. aedeagus lateral view; G. female seventh sternite, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242046/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Fig. 4E</figureCitation>
); slightly constricted laterally above median length (
<figureCitation id="51972A14FFE1FFE74EF3FD8DFBD89139" box="[949,1035,582,607]" captionStart="FIGURE4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[175,1419,1004,1816]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,988,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE4. Hecalus snipussp. nov. A.PygoPhore, lateral view; B. style, dorsal view; C.connective, dorsal view; D.valve and subgenital Plate, dorsal view; E. aedeagus, dorsal view; F. aedeagus lateral view; G. female seventh sternite, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242046/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="586">Fig. 4F</figureCitation>
). Gonopore subapical.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
